# Engineering Rules

- Respect the project stack and existing directory boundaries.
- Prefer small, reviewable changes with matching tests or validation commands.
- Do not commit secrets, local environment files, generated build output, or dependency folders.
- When changing templates, update README, AGENTS.md, and validation commands together.
- For bugs, reproduce or collect evidence before applying a fix.
